00:30:21.600 --> 00:30:26.120
So, when, let's say, you know,
you're an attorney or you're a doctor,

00:30:26.200 --> 00:30:28.760
and then there is an AI or consultant,

00:30:28.840 --> 00:30:34.320
and there is an AI model
that is trying to replicate

00:30:34.400 --> 00:30:37.040
