tasks that you do,

00:30:37.120 --> 00:30:40.560
there are always some corner cases,

00:30:40.640 --> 00:30:43.600
some exceptions
that the model by itself,

00:30:43.680 --> 00:30:45.280
even after you train it, you know,

00:30:45.360 --> 00:30:49.840
with all the world's data
that's available out there

00:30:49.920 --> 00:30:51.000
won't get to.

00:30:51.520 --> 00:30:57.640
So, when you recruit
