00:37:21.440 --> 00:37:26.280
accompany us for our daily task
is that we need to make them.

00:37:26.360 --> 00:37:30.000
So if you think about, you know,
the supply chain and everything required

00:37:30.080 --> 00:37:32.000
to make a gazillion of them,

00:37:32.080 --> 00:37:35.840
we might have AGI first,
you know, before robots actually

00:37:35.920 --> 00:37:38.480
started attacking us and taking over
the means of production.

00:37:38.560 --> 00:37:41.560
And the future, you know, might be bright,
you know, for them.

00:37:41.640 --> 00:37:43.800
But not as much for the human race.

00:37:43.880 --> 00:37:48.240
Just wanted to throw this out there
because I get a lot of people telling me,

00:37:48.320 --> 00:37:51.080
you know, who are not
as intimately familiar with AI telling me,

00:37:51.160 --> 00:37:52.880
"Oh, this is just pattern matching.

