02:51:59.280 --> 02:52:00.680
I wish I could act that well.

02:52:01.320 --> 02:52:04.000
So, actually, I think commented...

02:52:04.080 --> 02:52:06.480
or I sent him something
and I said "Great job."

02:52:06.560 --> 02:52:08.840
-I think he's doing a good job.
-[Deedy] That's nice.

02:52:08.920 --> 02:52:10.240
That's nice.

02:52:10.320 --> 02:52:12.720
-When are you inviting him to the podcast?
-[laughter]

02:52:12.800 --> 02:52:14.920
Someday soon. Why not, right?

